flowchart LR
  %% Revia Stitch - File Workspace (Viewer + Left Panel)

  A["File List View<br/>(Upload Files / Tech Packs)"] -->|Select file| B["File Workspace"]

  B --> C["Default: View<br/>Render full file inline<br/>(PDF/Excel)"]

  %% Left panel primary navigation/actions
  B --> H["Home<br/>(Style overview + activity)"]
  B --> V["View<br/>(read-only)"]
  B --> E["Edit<br/>(annotations, markups)"]
  B --> AU["Audit<br/>(consistency check)"]
  B --> CO["Collaborate<br/>(comments, mentions, resolve)"]
  B --> SH["Share<br/>(invite reviewers, permissions)"]
  B --> MG["Manage<br/>(metadata, tags, collection)"]
  B --> VR["Version History<br/>(immutable versions + diffs)"]
  B --> SG["Signature<br/>(approve/reject, sign-off)"]

  %% Common transitions
  E --> VR
  AU --> CO
  CO --> VR
  SG --> VR

  %% Guardrails
  B --> G{File status Ready?}
  G -->|No| AU2["Audit disabled<br/>(Indexing in progress)"]
  G -->|Yes| AU

